(8, 'Conflict Resolution Strategies, Motivational Factors and Job Involvement of Academic Staff of Private Universities', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:3.95pt;margin-right:110.35pt;\r\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:136.15pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Abstract</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:.1pt\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:.05pt;margin-right:24.95pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:8.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:\r\n-.5pt\">The study investigates the influence of Conflict Resolution Strategies\r\nand Motivational Factors on the Job Involvement of Academic Staff in Private\r\nUniversities in Oyo State. This study adopted a descriptive research design.\r\nThe population of the study consists of one thousand, two hundred and\r\nseventy-three (1273) academic staff of the 7 private universities in Oyo State,\r\nNigeria. All lecturers in the private universities in Oyo state were selected\r\nusing total enumeration. The data were analyzed using frequency, percentages\r\nand<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>inferential statistics of\r\nMultiple Regression analysis at a 0.05 level of significance. A self developed<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>instrument-<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.3pt\"> </span>Conflict<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>resolution<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>motivational<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.25pt\"> </span>factor,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.2pt\"> </span>job<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\"> </span>involvement<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span>questionnaire (CRMFJIQ) (=0.993) was used for data collection.\r\nThere was a significant combined influence of conflict strategies and\r\nmotivational factors on job involvement of academics <span style=\"position:\r\nrelative;top:-1.0pt;mso-text-raise:1.0pt\">staff in private universities in Oyo\r\nState (Adj.R<sup>2</sup>=0.991, F</span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt\">,<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>=<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>49730,<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span></span><span style=\"position:relative;top:-1.0pt;mso-text-raise:1.0pt\">P &lt; 0.05). The\r\nresult </span>showed that there was a moderate level (x=2.93) of job\r\ninvolvement of academic staff of private universities in Oyo State ; the most\r\ncommonly used Conflict Resolution strategy in private universities in Oyo State\r\nwas Negotiation (x=3.14) the level of Motivational Factor was moderate. Among\r\nconflict Resolution Strategies, collaboration has the highest positive impact\r\n(B = 1.221, Beta = 0.351), followed by mediation (B = 0.590, Beta = 0.154), and\r\naccommodation (B = 0.353, Beta = 0.081), Regarding motivational factors,\r\npromotion has the highest positive impact (B = 1.099, Beta = 0.234), followed\r\nby job security (B = 0.732, Beta = 0.187), and professional development\r\nopportunities (B = 0.108, Beta = 0.023). Academic staff in Oyo State private\r\nuniversities exhibit moderate level job involvement (x=2.93). Despite high\r\npromotion rates, areas for improvement include job security and professional\r\ndevelopment. To enhance negotiation capabilities and foster a positive work\r\nenvironment, private universities in Oyo State should invest in conflict\r\nresolution training<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.0pt\"> </span>for Academic\r\nStaff. A holistic approach to employee engagement is crucial, encompassing\r\ntransparent promotion processes, professional development opportunities, and\r\njob security measures to boost job involvement.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:12.85pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n0in;margin-left:7.5pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify\"><b>Keywords:<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.25pt\">\r\n</span></b>Job Involvement,<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>Conflict<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Resolution<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.1pt\"> </span>Strategies<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>and<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> </span>Motivational<span style=\"letter-spacing:\r\n-.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\">Factors.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<div class=\"WordSection1\">\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 5.85pt;\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:37.65pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"191\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:143.1pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;\r\n  height:37.65pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.3pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:2.5pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;letter-spacing:\r\n  -.1pt\">Title</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"285\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:214.05pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;\r\n  height:37.65pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:50.1pt;line-height:13.3pt;\r\n  mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">Table of<span style=\"letter-spacing:-.1pt\"> Content</span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"139\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:104.5pt;padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;\r\n  height:37.65pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"TableParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:6.3pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n  mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"Tab